Package: coinsndice
Title: Simulations of Statistical Inference via Coins and Dice
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("James", "Bernhard", , "jbernhard@projectivespace.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0009-0001-0762-2035"))
Description: Functions to simulate coins and dice, and to use these simulations to
    show what happens when statistical inference is repeated many times. This helps the
    user view p-values and the endpoints of confidence intervals as random variables.
License: CC BY 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
